
@ParcelManagement_HostAddress = https://localhost:5224

### Get all parcels
GET {{ParcelManagement_HostAddress}}/api/parcels
Accept: application/json

### Get parcel by id (replace with real Id from previous call)
GET {{ParcelManagement_HostAddress}}/api/parcels/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

### Create a new parcel
POST {{ParcelManagement_HostAddress}}/api/parcels
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

